dct_title_s: Plan of lots of the Beach Haven Land Company, Inc.
dct_description_sm: This map depicts a plan of lots of the Beach Haven Land Company between the Atlantic Ocean, Liberty Thorofare and Little Egg Harbor Bay. Several parcels are highlighted in red. The map is paper on linen, and has red/black print with penciled notes.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
